#. class="division">
msgctxt "dn5:1.1"
msgid "Dīgha Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Long Discourses 5"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "dn5:2.1"
msgid "Kūṭadantasutta"
msgstr "With Kūṭadanta"

#. </h1></div><h2>
msgctxt "dn5:3.1"
msgid "1. Khāṇumatakabrāhmaṇagahapatikā"
msgstr "The Brahmins and Householders of Khāṇumata"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a class="wp" id="wp1"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts1.127"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:4.1"
msgid "<span class=\"evam\">Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​</span>"
msgstr "<span class=”evam”>So I have heard.</span>"

msgctxt "dn5:4.2"
msgid ""
"ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā magadhesu cārikaṃ caramāno mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena "
"saddhiṃ pañcamattehi bhikkhusatehi yena khāṇumataṃ nāma magadhānaṃ "
"brāhmaṇagāmo tadavasari."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was wandering in the land of the Magadhans together "
"with a large Saṅgha of around five hundred mendicants when he arrived at "
"village of the Magadhan brahmins named Khāṇumata."

# RD has "pleasaunce", MW has "park" but the text has nothing.
msgctxt "dn5:4.3"
msgid "Tatra sudaṃ bhagavā khāṇumate viharati ambalaṭṭhikāyaṃ."
msgstr "There he stayed nearby at Ambalaṭṭhikā."

msgctxt "dn5:4.4"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena kūṭadanto brāhmaṇo khāṇumataṃ ajjhāvasati sattussadaṃ "
"satiṇakaṭṭhodakaṃ sadhaññaṃ rājabhoggaṃ raññā māgadhena seniyena bimbisārena "
"dinnaṃ rājadāyaṃ brahmadeyyaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Now at that time the brahmin Kūṭadanta was living in Khāṇumata. It was a "
"crown property given by King Seniya Bimbisāra of Magadha, teeming with "
"living creatures, full of hay, wood, water, and grain, a royal endowment of "
"the highest quality."

msgctxt "dn5:4.5"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena kūṭadantassa brāhmaṇassa mahāyañño upakkhaṭo hoti."
msgstr "Now at that time Kūṭadanta had prepared a great sacrifice."

msgctxt "dn5:4.6"
msgid ""
"Satta ca usabhasatāni satta ca vacchatarasatāni satta ca vacchatarīsatāni "
"satta ca ajasatāni satta ca urabbhasatāni thūṇūpanītāni honti yaññatthāya."
msgstr ""
"Bulls, bullocks, heifers, goats and rams—seven hundred of each—had been led "
"to the post for the sacrifice."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="wp" id="wp2"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts1.128"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:5.1"
msgid "Assosuṃ kho khāṇumatakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā:"
msgstr "The brahmins and householders of Khāṇumataka heard:"

msgctxt "dn5:5.2"
msgid ""
"“samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo sakyaputto sakyakulā pabbajito magadhesu cārikaṃ "
"caramāno mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ pañcamattehi bhikkhusatehi "
"khāṇumataṃ anuppatto khāṇumate viharati ambalaṭṭhikāyaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“It seems the ascetic Gotama—a Sakyan, gone forth from a Sakyan family—has "
"arrived at Khāṇumataka and is staying in a forest nearby."

msgctxt "dn5:5.3"
msgid "Taṃ kho pana bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ evaṃ kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggato:"
msgstr "He has this good reputation:"

msgctxt "dn5:5.4"
msgid ""
"‘itipi so bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho vijjācaraṇasampanno sugato lokavidū "
"anuttaro purisadammasārathi satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘That Blessed One is perfect, a fully awakened Buddha, accomplished in "
"knowledge and conduct, holy, knower of the world, supreme trainer of people, "
"teacher of gods and humans, awakened, blessed.’"

msgctxt "dn5:5.5"
msgid ""
"So imaṃ lokaṃ sadevakaṃ samārakaṃ sabrahmakaṃ sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiṃ pajaṃ "
"sadevamanussaṃ sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā pavedeti."
msgstr ""
"He has realized with his own insight this world—with its gods, Māras and "
"Brahmās, this population with its ascetics and brahmins, gods and humans—and "
"he makes it known to others."

msgctxt "dn5:5.6"
msgid ""
"So dhammaṃ deseti ādikalyāṇaṃ majjhekalyāṇaṃ pariyosānakalyāṇaṃ sātthaṃ "
"sabyañjanaṃ kevalaparipuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ pakāseti."
msgstr ""
"He teaches Dharma that’s good in the beginning, good in the middle, and good "
"in the end, meaningful and well-phrased. And he reveals a spiritual practice "
"that’s entirely full and pure."

msgctxt "dn5:5.7"
msgid "Sādhu kho pana tathārūpānaṃ arahataṃ dassanaṃ hotī”ti."
msgstr "It’s good to see such perfected ones.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a><a class="wp" id="wp3"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:6.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho khāṇumatakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā khāṇumatā nikkhamitvā saṅghasaṅghī "
"gaṇībhūtā yena ambalaṭṭhikā tenupasaṅkamanti."
msgstr ""
"Then, having departed Khāṇumataka, they formed into companies and headed to "
"Ambalaṭṭhikā."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="4"></a><a class="wp" id="wp4"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:7.1"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena kūṭadanto brāhmaṇo uparipāsāde divāseyyaṃ upagato "
"hoti."
msgstr ""
"Now at that time the brahmin Kūṭadanta had retired to the upper floor of his "
"stilt longhouse for his midday nap."

msgctxt "dn5:7.2"
msgid ""
"Addasā kho kūṭadanto brāhmaṇo khāṇumatake brāhmaṇagahapatike khāṇumatā "
"nikkhamitvā saṅghasaṅghī gaṇībhūte yena ambalaṭṭhikā tenupasaṅkamante."
msgstr "He saw the brahmins and householders heading for Ambalaṭṭhikā,"

msgctxt "dn5:7.3"
msgid "Disvā khattaṃ āmantesi:"
msgstr "and addressed his steward:"

msgctxt "dn5:7.4"
msgid ""
"“kiṃ nu kho, bho khatte, khāṇumatakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā khāṇumatā "
"nikkhamitvā saṅghasaṅghī gaṇībhūtā yena ambalaṭṭhikā tenupasaṅkamantī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“My steward, why are the brahmins and householders headed for the "
"Ambalaṭṭhikā?”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="5"></a><a class="wp" id="wp5"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:8.1"
msgid ""
"“Atthi kho, bho, samaṇo gotamo sakyaputto sakyakulā pabbajito magadhesu "
"cārikaṃ caramāno mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ pañcamattehi bhikkhusatehi "
"khāṇumataṃ anuppatto, khāṇumate viharati ambalaṭṭhikāyaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“The ascetic Gotama has arrived at Khāṇumataka and is staying at "
"Ambalaṭṭhikā."

msgctxt "dn5:8.2"
msgid "Taṃ kho pana bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ evaṃ kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggato:"
msgstr "He has this good reputation:"

msgctxt "dn5:8.3"
msgid ""
"‘itipi so bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho vijjācaraṇasampanno sugato lokavidū "
"anuttaro purisadammasārathi satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘That Blessed One is perfect, a fully awakened Buddha, accomplished in "
"knowledge and conduct, holy, knower of the world, supreme trainer of people, "
"teacher of gods and humans, awakened, blessed.’"

msgctxt "dn5:8.4"
msgid "Tamete bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamantī”ti."
msgstr "They’re going to see that Master Gotama.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="6"></a><a class="wp" id="wp6"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts1.129"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:9.1"
msgid "Atha kho kūṭadantassa brāhmaṇassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Kūṭadanta thought:"

msgctxt "dn5:9.2"
msgid "“sutaṃ kho pana metaṃ:"
msgstr "“I’ve heard that"

msgctxt "dn5:9.3"
msgid "‘samaṇo gotamo tividhaṃ yaññasampadaṃ soḷasaparikkhāraṃ jānātī’ti."
msgstr ""
"the ascetic Gotama knows how to accomplish the sacrifice with three modes "
"and sixteen accessories."

msgctxt "dn5:9.4"
msgid "Na kho panāhaṃ jānāmi tividhaṃ yaññasampadaṃ soḷasaparikkhāraṃ."
msgstr "I don’t know about that,"

msgctxt "dn5:9.5"
msgid "Icchāmi cāhaṃ mahāyaññaṃ yajituṃ."
msgstr "but I wish to perform a great sacrifice."

msgctxt "dn5:9.6"
msgid ""
"Yannūnāhaṃ samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ upasaṅkamitvā tividhaṃ yaññasampadaṃ "
"soḷasaparikkhāraṃ puccheyyan”ti."
msgstr ""
"Why don’t I ask him how to accomplish the sacrifice with three modes and "
"sixteen accessories?”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="7"></a><a class="wp" id="wp7"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:10.1"
msgid "Atha kho kūṭadanto brāhmaṇo khattaṃ āmantesi:"
msgstr "Then Kūṭadanta addressed his steward:"

msgctxt "dn5:10.2"
msgid ""
"“tena hi, bho khatte, yena khāṇumatakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā tenupasaṅkama."
msgstr "“Well then, go to the brahmins and householders say to them:"

msgctxt "dn5:10.3"
msgid "Upasaṅkamitvā khāṇumatake brāhmaṇagahapatike evaṃ vadehi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:10.4"
msgid "‘kūṭadanto, bho, brāhmaṇo evamāha—"
msgstr "“Sirs, the brahmin Kūṭadanta asks"

msgctxt "dn5:10.5"
msgid ""
"āgamentu kira bhavanto, kūṭadantopi brāhmaṇo samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya "
"upasaṅkamissatī’”ti."
msgstr "you to wait, as he will also go to see the ascetic Gotama.’”"

msgctxt "dn5:10.6"
msgid ""
"“Evaṃ, bho”ti kho so khattā kūṭadantassa brāhmaṇassa paṭissutvā yena "
"khāṇumatakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā tenupasaṅkami."
msgstr "“Yes, sir,” replied the steward, and did as he was asked."

msgctxt "dn5:10.7"
msgid "Upasaṅkamitvā khāṇumatake brāhmaṇagahapatike etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:10.8"
msgid "“kūṭadanto, bho, brāhmaṇo evamāha:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:10.9"
msgid ""
"‘āgamentu kira bhonto, kūṭadantopi brāhmaṇo samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya "
"upasaṅkamissatī’”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn5:11.1"
msgid "2. Kūṭadantaguṇakathā"
msgstr "The Qualities of Kūṭadanta"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="8"></a><a class="wp" id="wp8"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:12.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena anekāni brāhmaṇasatāni khāṇumate paṭivasanti:"
msgstr "Now at that time several hundred brahmins were residing in Khāṇumata"

msgctxt "dn5:12.2"
msgid "“kūṭadantassa brāhmaṇassa mahāyaññaṃ anubhavissāmā”ti."
msgstr "thinking to participate in Kūṭadanta’s sacrifice."

msgctxt "dn5:12.3"
msgid "Assosuṃ kho te brāhmaṇā:"
msgstr "They heard that"

msgctxt "dn5:12.4"
msgid "“kūṭadanto kira brāhmaṇo samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamissatī”ti."
msgstr "Kūṭadanta was going to see the ascetic Gotama."

msgctxt "dn5:12.5"
msgid "Atha kho te brāhmaṇā yena kūṭadanto brāhmaṇo tenupasaṅkamiṃsu."
msgstr "They approached Kūṭadanta"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="9"></a><a class="wp" id="wp9"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:13.1"
msgid "Upasaṅkamitvā kūṭadantaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ etadavocuṃ:"
msgstr "and said to him:"

msgctxt "dn5:13.2"
msgid ""
"“saccaṃ kira bhavaṃ kūṭadanto samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamissatī”ti?"
msgstr "“Is it really true that you are going to see the ascetic Gotama?”"

msgctxt "dn5:13.3"
msgid "“Evaṃ kho me, bho, hoti:"
msgstr "“Yes, gentlemen, it is true.”"

msgctxt "dn5:13.4"
msgid "‘ahampi samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamissāmī’”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="10"></a><a class="wp" id="wp10"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts1.130"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:14.1"
msgid "“Mā bhavaṃ kūṭadanto samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkami."
msgstr "“Please don’t!"

msgctxt "dn5:14.2"
msgid "Na arahati bhavaṃ kūṭadanto samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamituṃ."
msgstr "It’s not appropriate for you to go to see the ascetic Gotama."

msgctxt "dn5:14.3"
msgid ""
"Sace bhavaṃ kūṭadanto samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamissati, bhoto "
"kūṭadantassa yaso hāyissati, samaṇassa gotamassa yaso abhivaḍḍhissati."
msgstr "For if you do so, your reputation will diminish and his will increase."

msgctxt "dn5:14.4"
msgid ""
"Yampi bhoto kūṭadantassa yaso hāyissati, samaṇassa gotamassa yaso "
"abhivaḍḍhissati, imināpaṅgena na arahati bhavaṃ kūṭadanto samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ "
"dassanāya upasaṅkamituṃ."
msgstr ""
"For this reason it’s not appropriate for you to go to see the ascetic Gotama;"

msgctxt "dn5:14.5"
msgid ""
"Samaṇo tveva gotamo arahati bhavantaṃ kūṭadantaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamituṃ."
msgstr "it’s appropriate that he comes to see you."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="11"></a><a class="wp" id="wp11"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:15.1"
msgid ""
"Bhavañhi kūṭadanto ubhato sujāto mātito ca pitito ca saṃsuddhagahaṇiko yāva "
"sattamā pitāmahayugā akkhitto anupakkuṭṭho jātivādena."
msgstr ""
"You are well born on both your mother’s and father’s side, of pure descent, "
"irrefutable and impeccable in questions of ancestry back to the seventh "
"paternal generation."

msgctxt "dn5:15.2"
msgid ""
"Yampi bhavaṃ kūṭadanto ubhato sujāto mātito ca pitito ca saṃsuddhagahaṇiko "
"yāva sattamā pitāmahayugā akkhitto anupakkuṭṭho jātivādena, imināpaṅgena na "
"arahati bhavaṃ kūṭadanto samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamituṃ."
msgstr ""
"For this reason it’s not appropriate for you to go to see the ascetic Gotama;"

msgctxt "dn5:15.3"
msgid ""
"Samaṇo tveva gotamo arahati bhavantaṃ kūṭadantaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamituṃ."
msgstr "it’s appropriate that he comes to see you."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="12"></a><a class="wp" id="wp12"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:16.1"
msgid ""
"Bhavañhi kūṭadanto aḍḍho mahaddhano mahābhogo pahūtavittūpakaraṇo "
"pahūtajātarūparajato …"
msgstr ""
"You’re rich, affluent, and wealthy, with lots of property and assets, and "
"lots of money and grain …"

msgctxt "dn5:16.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="13"></a><a class="wp" id="wp13"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:17.1"
msgid ""
"Bhavañhi kūṭadanto ajjhāyako mantadharo tiṇṇaṃ vedānaṃ pāragū "
"sanighaṇḍukeṭubhānaṃ sākkharappabhedānaṃ itihāsapañcamānaṃ padako "
"veyyākaraṇo lokāyatamahāpurisalakkhaṇesu anavayo …"
msgstr ""
"You recite and remember the hymns, and are an expert in the three Vedas, "
"together with their vocabularies, ritual, phonology and etymology, and the "
"testament as fifth. You know philology and grammar, and are well versed in "
"cosmology and the marks of a great man. …"

msgctxt "dn5:17.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="14"></a><a class="wp" id="wp14"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:18.1"
msgid ""
"Bhavañhi kūṭadanto abhirūpo dassanīyo pāsādiko paramāya vaṇṇapokkharatāya "
"samannāgato brahmavaṇṇī brahmavacchasī akhuddāvakāso dassanāya …"
msgstr ""
"You are attractive, good-looking, lovely, of surpassing beauty. You are "
"magnificent, splendid, remarkable to behold. …"

msgctxt "dn5:18.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="15"></a><a class="wp" id="wp15"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:19.1"
msgid "Bhavañhi kūṭadanto sīlavā vuddhasīlī vuddhasīlena samannāgato …"
msgstr "You are ethical, mature in ethical conduct. …"

msgctxt "dn5:19.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="16"></a><a class="wp" id="wp16"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:20.1"
msgid ""
"Bhavañhi kūṭadanto kalyāṇavāco kalyāṇavākkaraṇo poriyā vācāya samannāgato "
"vissaṭṭhāya anelagalāya atthassa viññāpaniyā …"
msgstr ""
"You’re a good speaker, with a polished, clear, and articulate voice that "
"expresses the meaning. …"

msgctxt "dn5:20.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="17"></a><a class="wp" id="wp17"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:21.1"
msgid ""
"Bhavañhi kūṭadanto bahūnaṃ ācariyapācariyo tīṇi māṇavakasatāni mante vāceti, "
"bahū kho pana nānādisā nānājanapadā māṇavakā āgacchanti bhoto kūṭadantassa "
"santike mantatthikā mante adhiyitukāmā …"
msgstr ""
"You teach the teachers of many, and teach three hundred students to recite "
"the hymns. Many students come from various districts and countries for the "
"sake of the hymns, wishing to learn the hymns. …"

msgctxt "dn5:21.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="18"></a><a class="wp" id="wp18"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:22.1"
msgid "Bhavañhi kūṭadanto jiṇṇo vuddho mahallako addhagato vayoanuppatto."
msgstr ""
"You’re old, elderly and senior, advanced in years, and have reached the "
"final stage of life."

msgctxt "dn5:22.2"
msgid "Samaṇo gotamo taruṇo ceva taruṇapabbajito ca …"
msgstr "The ascetic Gotama is young, and has newly gone forth. …"

msgctxt "dn5:22.3"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="19"></a><a class="wp" id="wp19"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:23.1"
msgid ""
"Bhavañhi kūṭadanto rañño māgadhassa seniyassa bimbisārassa sakkato garukato "
"mānito pūjito apacito …"
msgstr ""
"You’re honored, respected, revered, venerated, and esteemed by King "
"Bimbisāra of Magadha …"

msgctxt "dn5:23.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="20"></a><a class="wp" id="wp20"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:24.1"
msgid ""
"Bhavañhi kūṭadanto brāhmaṇassa pokkharasātissa sakkato garukato mānito "
"pūjito apacito …"
msgstr "and the brahmin Pokkarasāti. …"

msgctxt "dn5:24.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="21"></a><a class="wp" id="wp21"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts1.131"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:25.1"
msgid ""
"Bhavañhi kūṭadanto khāṇumataṃ ajjhāvasati sattussadaṃ satiṇakaṭṭhodakaṃ "
"sadhaññaṃ rājabhoggaṃ raññā māgadhena seniyena bimbisārena dinnaṃ rājadāyaṃ "
"brahmadeyyaṃ."
msgstr ""
"You live in Khāṇumata, a crown property given by King Seniya Bimbisāra of "
"Magadha, teeming with living creatures, full of hay, wood, water, and grain, "
"a royal endowment of the highest quality."

msgctxt "dn5:25.2"
msgid ""
"Yampi bhavaṃ kūṭadanto khāṇumataṃ ajjhāvasati sattussadaṃ satiṇakaṭṭhodakaṃ "
"sadhaññaṃ rājabhoggaṃ, raññā māgadhena seniyena bimbisārena dinnaṃ rājadāyaṃ "
"brahmadeyyaṃ, imināpaṅgena na arahati bhavaṃ kūṭadanto samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ "
"dassanāya upasaṅkamituṃ."
msgstr ""
"For this reason it’s not appropriate for you to go to see the ascetic Gotama;"

msgctxt "dn5:25.3"
msgid ""
"Samaṇo tveva gotamo arahati bhavantaṃ kūṭadantaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamitun”ti."
msgstr "it’s appropriate that he comes to see you."

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn5:26.1"
msgid "3. Buddhaguṇakathā"
msgstr "The Qualities of the Buddha"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="22"></a><a class="wp" id="wp22"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:27.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, kūṭadanto brāhmaṇo te brāhmaṇe etadavoca:"
msgstr "When they had spoken, Kūṭadanta said to those brahmins:"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="23"></a>
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "dn5:28.1"
msgid ""
"“Tena hi, bho, mamapi suṇātha, yathā mayameva arahāma taṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ "
"dassanāya upasaṅkamituṃ, na tveva arahati so bhavaṃ gotamo amhākaṃ dassanāya "
"upasaṅkamituṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Well then, gentlemen, listen to why it’s appropriate for me to go to see "
"the ascetic Gotama, and it’s not appropriate for him to come to see me."

msgctxt "dn5:28.2"
msgid ""
"Samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo ubhato sujāto mātito ca pitito ca "
"saṃsuddhagahaṇiko yāva sattamā pitāmahayugā akkhitto anupakkuṭṭho jātivādena."
msgstr ""
"He is well born on both his mother’s and father’s side, of pure descent, "
"irrefutable and impeccable in questions of ancestry back to the seventh "
"paternal generation."

msgctxt "dn5:28.3"
msgid ""
"Yampi, bho, samaṇo gotamo ubhato sujāto mātito ca pitito ca "
"saṃsuddhagahaṇiko yāva sattamā pitāmahayugā akkhitto anupakkuṭṭho "
"jātivādena, imināpaṅgena na arahati so bhavaṃ gotamo amhākaṃ dassanāya "
"upasaṅkamituṃ."
msgstr ""
"For this reason it’s not appropriate for the ascetic Gotama to come to see "
"me;"

msgctxt "dn5:28.4"
msgid ""
"Atha kho mayameva arahāma taṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamituṃ."
msgstr "rather, it’s appropriate for me to go to see him."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="24"></a><a class="wp" id="wp24"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:29.1"
msgid "Samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo mahantaṃ ñātisaṅghaṃ ohāya pabbajito …"
msgstr "When he went forth he abandoned a large family circle. …"

msgctxt "dn5:29.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="25"></a><a class="wp" id="wp25"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:30.1"
msgid ""
"Samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo pahūtaṃ hiraññasuvaṇṇaṃ ohāya pabbajito "
"bhūmigatañca vehāsaṭṭhaṃ ca …"
msgstr ""
"When he went forth he abandoned abundant gold coin and bullion stored in "
"dungeons and towers. …"

msgctxt "dn5:30.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="26"></a><a class="wp" id="wp26"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:31.1"
msgid ""
"Samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo daharova samāno yuvā susukāḷakeso bhadrena "
"yobbanena samannāgato paṭhamena vayasā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito …"
msgstr ""
"He went forth from the lay life to homelessness while still a youth, young, "
"black-haired, blessed with youth, in the prime of life. …"

msgctxt "dn5:31.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="27"></a><a class="wp" id="wp27"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:32.1"
msgid ""
"Samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo akāmakānaṃ mātāpitūnaṃ assumukhānaṃ rudantānaṃ "
"kesamassuṃ ohāretvā kāsāyāni vatthāni acchādetvā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ "
"pabbajito …"
msgstr ""
"Though his mother and father wished otherwise, weeping with tearful faces, "
"he shaved off his hair and beard, dressed in ochre robes, and went forth "
"from the lay life into homelessness. …"

msgctxt "dn5:32.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="28"></a><a class="wp" id="wp28"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts1.132"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:33.1"
msgid ""
"Samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo abhirūpo dassanīyo pāsādiko paramāya "
"vaṇṇapokkharatāya samannāgato brahmavaṇṇī brahmavacchasī akhuddāvakāso "
"dassanāya …"
msgstr ""
"He is attractive, good-looking, lovely, of surpassing beauty. He is "
"magnificent, splendid, remarkable to behold. …"

msgctxt "dn5:33.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="29"></a><a class="wp" id="wp29"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:34.1"
msgid ""
"Samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo sīlavā ariyasīlī kusalasīlī kusalasīlena "
"samannāgato …"
msgstr "He is ethical, possessing ethical conduct that is noble and skilful. …"

msgctxt "dn5:34.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="30"></a><a class="wp" id="wp30"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:35.1"
msgid ""
"Samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo kalyāṇavāco kalyāṇavākkaraṇo poriyā vācāya "
"samannāgato vissaṭṭhāya anelagalāya atthassa viññāpaniyā …"
msgstr ""
"He’s a good speaker, with a polished, clear, and articulate voice that "
"expresses the meaning. …"

msgctxt "dn5:35.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="31"></a><a class="wp" id="wp31"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:36.1"
msgid "Samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo bahūnaṃ ācariyapācariyo …"
msgstr "He’s a teacher of teachers. …"

msgctxt "dn5:36.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="32"></a><a class="wp" id="wp32"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:37.1"
msgid "Samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo khīṇakāmarāgo vigatacāpallo …"
msgstr "He has ended sensual desire, and is rid of caprice. …"

msgctxt "dn5:37.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="33"></a><a class="wp" id="wp33"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:38.1"
msgid ""
"Samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo kammavādī kiriyavādī apāpapurekkhāro brahmaññāya "
"pajāya …"
msgstr ""
"He teaches the efficacy of deeds and action. He doesn’t wish any harm upon "
"the community of brahmins. …"

msgctxt "dn5:38.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="34"></a><a class="wp" id="wp34"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:39.1"
msgid "Samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo uccā kulā pabbajito asambhinnakhattiyakulā …"
msgstr ""
"He went forth from an eminent family of unbroken aristocratic lineage. …"

msgctxt "dn5:39.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="35"></a><a class="wp" id="wp35"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:40.1"
msgid "Samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo aḍḍhā kulā pabbajito mahaddhanā mahābhogā …"
msgstr "He went forth from a rich, affluent, and wealthy family. …"

msgctxt "dn5:40.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="36"></a><a class="wp" id="wp36"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:41.1"
msgid ""
"Samaṇaṃ khalu, bho, gotamaṃ tiroraṭṭhā tirojanapadā pañhaṃ pucchituṃ "
"āgacchanti …"
msgstr "People come from distant lands and distant countries to question him. …"

msgctxt "dn5:41.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="37"></a><a class="wp" id="wp37"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:42.1"
msgid ""
"Samaṇaṃ khalu, bho, gotamaṃ anekāni devatāsahassāni pāṇehi saraṇaṃ gatāni …"
msgstr "Many thousands of deities have gone for refuge for life to him. …"

msgctxt "dn5:42.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="38"></a><a class="wp" id="wp38"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:43.1"
msgid "Samaṇaṃ khalu, bho, gotamaṃ evaṃ kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggato:"
msgstr "He has this good reputation:"

msgctxt "dn5:43.2"
msgid ""
"‘itipi so bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho vijjācaraṇasampanno sugato lokavidū "
"anuttaro purisadammasārathi satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā’ti …"
msgstr ""
"‘That Blessed One is perfect, a fully awakened Buddha, accomplished in "
"knowledge and conduct, holy, knower of the world, supreme trainer of people, "
"teacher of gods and humans, awakened, blessed.’ …"

msgctxt "dn5:43.3"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="39"></a><a class="wp" id="wp39"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:44.1"
msgid "Samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo dvattiṃsamahāpurisalakkhaṇehi samannāgato …"
msgstr "He has the thirty-two marks of a great man. …"

msgctxt "dn5:44.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="40"></a><a class="wp" id="wp40"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:45.1"
msgid ""
"Samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo ehisvāgatavādī sakhilo sammodako abbhākuṭiko "
"uttānamukho pubbabhāsī …"
msgstr ""
"He is welcoming, congenial, polite, smiling, open, the first to speak. …"

msgctxt "dn5:45.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="41"></a><a class="wp" id="wp41"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:46.1"
msgid ""
"Samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo catunnaṃ parisānaṃ sakkato garukato mānito pūjito "
"apacito …"
msgstr ""
"He’s honored, respected, revered, venerated, and esteemed by the four "
"assemblies. …"

msgctxt "dn5:46.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="42"></a><a class="wp" id="wp42"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:47.1"
msgid "Samaṇe khalu, bho, gotame bahū devā ca manussā ca abhippasannā …"
msgstr "Many gods and humans are devoted to him. …"

msgctxt "dn5:47.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="43"></a><a class="wp" id="wp43"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:48.1"
msgid ""
"Samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo yasmiṃ gāme vā nigame vā paṭivasati na tasmiṃ gāme "
"vā nigame vā amanussā manusse viheṭhenti …"
msgstr ""
"While he is residing in a village or town, non-human entities do not harass "
"them. …"

msgctxt "dn5:48.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="44"></a><a class="wp" id="wp44"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:49.1"
msgid ""
"Samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo saṅghī gaṇī gaṇācariyo puthutitthakarānaṃ "
"aggamakkhāyati, yathā kho pana, bho, etesaṃ samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ yathā vā tathā "
"vā yaso samudāgacchati, na hevaṃ samaṇassa gotamassa yaso samudāgato."
msgstr ""
"He leads an order and a community, and teaches a community, and is said to "
"be the best of the various religious founders. He didn’t come by his fame in "
"the same ways as those other ascetics and brahmins."

msgctxt "dn5:49.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho anuttarāya vijjācaraṇasampadāya samaṇassa gotamassa yaso samudāgato "
"…"
msgstr "Rather, he came by his fame due to his supreme knowledge and conduct. …"

msgctxt "dn5:49.3"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="45"></a><a class="wp" id="wp45"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts1.133"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:50.1"
msgid ""
"Samaṇaṃ khalu, bho, gotamaṃ rājā māgadho seniyo bimbisāro saputto sabhariyo "
"sapariso sāmacco pāṇehi saraṇaṃ gato …"
msgstr ""
"King Seniya Bimbisāra of Magadha and his wives and children have gone for "
"refuge for life to the ascetic Gotama. …"

msgctxt "dn5:50.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="46"></a><a class="wp" id="wp46"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:51.1"
msgid ""
"Samaṇaṃ khalu, bho, gotamaṃ rājā pasenadi kosalo saputto sabhariyo sapariso "
"sāmacco pāṇehi saraṇaṃ gato …"
msgstr ""
"King Pasenadi of Kosala and his wives and children have gone for refuge for "
"life to the ascetic Gotama. …"

msgctxt "dn5:51.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="47"></a><a class="wp" id="wp47"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:52.1"
msgid ""
"Samaṇaṃ khalu, bho, gotamaṃ brāhmaṇo pokkharasāti saputto sabhariyo sapariso "
"sāmacco pāṇehi saraṇaṃ gato …"
msgstr ""
"The brahmin Pokkharasāti and his wives and children have gone for refuge for "
"life to the ascetic Gotama. …"

msgctxt "dn5:52.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="48"></a><a class="wp" id="wp48"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:53.1"
msgid ""
"Samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo rañño māgadhassa seniyassa bimbisārassa sakkato "
"garukato mānito pūjito apacito …"
msgstr ""
"He’s honored, respected, revered, venerated, and esteemed by King Bimbisāra "
"of Magadha …"

msgctxt "dn5:53.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="49"></a><a class="wp" id="wp49"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:54.1"
msgid ""
"Samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo rañño pasenadissa kosalassa sakkato garukato "
"mānito pūjito apacito …"
msgstr "King Pasenadi of Kosala …"

msgctxt "dn5:54.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="50"></a><a class="wp" id="wp50"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:55.1"
msgid ""
"Samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo brāhmaṇassa pokkharasātissa sakkato garukato "
"mānito pūjito apacito …"
msgstr "and the brahmin Pokkarasāti."

msgctxt "dn5:55.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="51"></a><a class="wp" id="wp51"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:56.1"
msgid ""
"Samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo khāṇumataṃ anuppatto khāṇumate viharati "
"ambalaṭṭhikāyaṃ."
msgstr ""
"The ascetic Gotama has arrived at Khāṇumata and is staying at Ambalaṭṭhikā."

msgctxt "dn5:56.2"
msgid ""
"Ye kho pana, bho, keci samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā amhākaṃ gāmakhettaṃ āgacchanti, "
"atithī no te honti."
msgstr ""
"Any ascetic or brahmin who comes to stay in our village district is our "
"guest,"

msgctxt "dn5:56.3"
msgid ""
"Atithī kho panamhehi sakkātabbā garukātabbā mānetabbā pūjetabbā apacetabbā."
msgstr "and should be honored and respected as such."

msgctxt "dn5:56.4"
msgid ""
"Yampi, bho, samaṇo gotamo khāṇumataṃ anuppatto khāṇumate viharati "
"ambalaṭṭhikāyaṃ, atithimhākaṃ samaṇo gotamo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:56.5"
msgid ""
"Atithi kho panamhehi sakkātabbo garukātabbo mānetabbo pūjetabbo apacetabbo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:56.6"
msgid "Imināpaṅgena nārahati so bhavaṃ gotamo amhākaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamituṃ."
msgstr ""
"For this reason, too, it’s not appropriate for Master Gotama to come to see "
"me,"

msgctxt "dn5:56.7"
msgid ""
"Atha kho mayameva arahāma taṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamituṃ."
msgstr "rather, it’s appropriate for me to go to see him."

msgctxt "dn5:56.8"
msgid ""
"Ettake kho ahaṃ, bho, tassa bhoto gotamassa vaṇṇe pariyāpuṇāmi, no ca kho so "
"bhavaṃ gotamo ettakavaṇṇo."
msgstr ""
"This is the extent of Master Gotama’s praise that I have learned. But his "
"praises are not confined to this,"

msgctxt "dn5:56.9"
msgid "Aparimāṇavaṇṇo hi so bhavaṃ gotamo”ti."
msgstr "for the praise of Master Gotama is limitless.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="52"></a><a class="wp" id="wp52"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:57.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, te brāhmaṇā kūṭadantaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ etadavocuṃ:"
msgstr "When he had spoken, those brahmins said to him:"

msgctxt "dn5:57.2"
msgid ""
"“yathā kho bhavaṃ kūṭadanto samaṇassa gotamassa vaṇṇe bhāsati, ito cepi so "
"bhavaṃ gotamo yojanasate viharati, alameva saddhena kulaputtena dassanāya "
"upasaṅkamituṃ api puṭosenā”ti."
msgstr ""
"“According to Kūṭadanta’s praises, if Master Gotama was staying within a "
"hundred leagues, it’d be worthwhile for a faithful person of respectable "
"family to go to see him, even if they had to carry their own provisions in a "
"shoulder bag.”"

msgctxt "dn5:57.3"
msgid ""
"“Tena hi, bho, sabbeva mayaṃ samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamissāmā”ti."
msgstr "“Well then, gentlemen, let’s all go to see the ascetic Gotama.”"

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn5:58.1"
msgid "4. Mahāvijitarājayaññakathā"
msgstr "The Story of King Mahāvijita’s Sacrifice"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="53"></a><a class="wp" id="wp53"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts1.134"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:59.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho kūṭadanto brāhmaṇo mahatā brāhmaṇagaṇena saddhiṃ yena ambalaṭṭhikā "
"yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami, upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi."
msgstr ""
"Then Kūṭadanta together with a large group of brahmins went to see the "
"Buddha and exchanged greetings with him. "

msgctxt "dn5:59.2"
msgid "Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi."
msgstr ""
"When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one "
"side."

msgctxt "dn5:59.3"
msgid ""
"Khāṇumatakāpi kho brāhmaṇagahapatikā appekacce bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā "
"ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu;"
msgstr ""
"Before sitting down to one side, some of the brahmins and householders of "
"Campā bowed, some exchanged greetings and polite conversation, some held up "
"their cupped palms toward the Buddha, some announced their name and clan, "
"while some kept silent."

msgctxt "dn5:59.4"
msgid ""
"appekacce bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodiṃsu, sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ "
"vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:59.5"
msgid "appekacce yena bhagavā tenañjaliṃ paṇāmetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:59.6"
msgid "appekacce nāmagottaṃ sāvetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:59.7"
msgid "appekacce tuṇhībhūtā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="54"></a><a class="wp" id="wp54"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:60.1"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho kūṭadanto brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Kūṭadanta said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "dn5:60.2"
msgid "“sutaṃ metaṃ, bho gotama:"
msgstr "“Master Gotama, I’ve heard that"

msgctxt "dn5:60.3"
msgid "‘samaṇo gotamo tividhaṃ yaññasampadaṃ soḷasaparikkhāraṃ jānātī’ti."
msgstr ""
"you know how to accomplish the sacrifice with three modes and sixteen "
"accessories."

msgctxt "dn5:60.4"
msgid "Na kho panāhaṃ jānāmi tividhaṃ yaññasampadaṃ soḷasaparikkhāraṃ."
msgstr "I don’t know about that,"

msgctxt "dn5:60.5"
msgid "Icchāmi cāhaṃ mahāyaññaṃ yajituṃ."
msgstr "but I wish to perform a great sacrifice."

msgctxt "dn5:60.6"
msgid ""
"Sādhu me bhavaṃ gotamo tividhaṃ yaññasampadaṃ soḷasaparikkhāraṃ desetū”ti."
msgstr ""
"Please teach me how to accomplish the sacrifice with three modes and sixteen "
"accessories.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="55"></a><a class="wp" id="wp55"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:61.1"
msgid "“Tena hi, brāhmaṇa, suṇāhi sādhukaṃ manasikarohi, bhāsissāmī”ti."
msgstr "“Well then, mendicants, listen and pay close attention, I will speak.”"

msgctxt "dn5:61.2"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bho”ti kho kūṭadanto brāhmaṇo bhagavato paccassosi."
msgstr "“Yes sir,” Kūṭadanta replied. "

msgctxt "dn5:61.3"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr "The Buddha said this:"

msgctxt "dn5:61.4"
msgid ""
"“bhūtapubbaṃ, brāhmaṇa, rājā mahāvijito nāma ahosi aḍḍho mahaddhano "
"mahābhogo pahūtajātarūparajato pahūtavittūpakaraṇo pahūtadhanadhañño "
"paripuṇṇakosakoṭṭhāgāro."
msgstr ""
"Once upon a time, brahmin, there was a king named Mahāvijita. He was rich, "
"affluent, and wealthy, with lots of gold and silver, lots of property and "
"assets, lots of money and grain, and a full treasury and storehouses."

msgctxt "dn5:61.5"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, brāhmaṇa, rañño mahāvijitassa rahogatassa paṭisallīnassa evaṃ "
"cetaso parivitakko udapādi:"
msgstr ""
"Then as King Mahāvijita was in private solitude this thought came to his "
"mind: "

msgctxt "dn5:61.6"
msgid ""
"‘adhigatā kho me vipulā mānusakā bhogā, mahantaṃ pathavimaṇḍalaṃ abhivijiya "
"ajjhāvasāmi, yannūnāhaṃ mahāyaññaṃ yajeyyaṃ, yaṃ mama assa dīgharattaṃ "
"hitāya sukhāyā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I have achieved human wealth, and reign after conquering this great land. "
"Why don’t I hold a large sacrifice? That will be for my lasting welfare and "
"happiness.’"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="56"></a><a class="wp" id="wp56"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts1.135"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:62.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, brāhmaṇa, rājā mahāvijito purohitaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ āmantetvā etadavoca:"
msgstr "Then he summoned the brahmin high priest and said to him:"

msgctxt "dn5:62.2"
msgid ""
"‘idha mayhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, rahogatassa paṭisallīnassa evaṃ cetaso parivitakko "
"udapādi:"
msgstr ""
"‘Just now, brahmin, as I was in private solitude this thought came to mind:"

msgctxt "dn5:62.3"
msgid ""
"“adhigatā kho me vipulā mānusakā bhogā, mahantaṃ pathavimaṇḍalaṃ abhivijiya "
"ajjhāvasāmi."
msgstr ""
"“I have achieved human wealth, and reign after conquering this great land. "
"Why don’t I perform a great sacrifice? That will be for my lasting welfare "
"and happiness.”"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "dn5:62.4"
msgid ""
"Yannūnāhaṃ mahāyaññaṃ yajeyyaṃ yaṃ mama assa dīgharattaṃ hitāya sukhāyā”ti."
msgstr " "

msgctxt "dn5:62.5"
msgid "Icchāmahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, mahāyaññaṃ yajituṃ."
msgstr "Brahmin, I wish to perform a great sacrifice."

msgctxt "dn5:62.6"
msgid "Anusāsatu maṃ bhavaṃ yaṃ mama assa dīgharattaṃ hitāya sukhāyā’ti."
msgstr "Please instruct me. It will be for my lasting welfare and happiness.’"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="57"></a><a class="wp" id="wp57"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts1.136"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:63.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, brāhmaṇa, purohito brāhmaṇo rājānaṃ mahāvijitaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he had spoken, the brahmin high priest said to him:"

msgctxt "dn5:63.2"
msgid ""
"‘bhoto kho rañño janapado sakaṇṭako sauppīḷo, gāmaghātāpi dissanti, "
"nigamaghātāpi dissanti, nagaraghātāpi dissanti, panthaduhanāpi dissanti."
msgstr ""
"‘Sir, the king’s realm is harried and oppressed. Bandits have been seen "
"raiding villages, town, and cities, and infesting the highways."

msgctxt "dn5:63.3"
msgid ""
"Bhavaṃ kho pana rājā evaṃ sakaṇṭake janapade sauppīḷe balimuddhareyya, "
"akiccakārī assa tena bhavaṃ rājā."
msgstr ""
"But if the king were to extract more taxes while his realm is thus harried "
"and oppressed, he would not be doing his duty."

msgctxt "dn5:63.4"
msgid "Siyā kho pana bhoto rañño evamassa:"
msgstr "Now the king might think:"

msgctxt "dn5:63.5"
msgid ""
"“ahametaṃ dassukhīlaṃ vadhena vā bandhena vā jāniyā vā garahāya vā "
"pabbājanāya vā samūhanissāmī”ti, na kho panetassa dassukhīlassa evaṃ sammā "
"samugghāto hoti."
msgstr ""
"“I’ll uproot this barbarian obstacle by execution or imprisonment or "
"condemnation or banishment!” But that’s not the right way to uproot this "
"barbarian obstacle."

msgctxt "dn5:63.6"
msgid ""
"Ye te hatāvasesakā bhavissanti, te pacchā rañño janapadaṃ viheṭhessanti."
msgstr ""
"Those who remain after the killing will return to harass the king’s realm."

msgctxt "dn5:63.7"
msgid ""
"Api ca kho idaṃ saṃvidhānaṃ āgamma evametassa dassukhīlassa sammā samugghāto "
"hoti."
msgstr ""
"Rather, here is a plan, relying on which the barbarian obstacle will be "
"properly uprooted."

msgctxt "dn5:63.8"
msgid ""
"Tena hi bhavaṃ rājā ye bhoto rañño janapade ussahanti kasigorakkhe, tesaṃ "
"bhavaṃ rājā bījabhattaṃ anuppadetu."
msgstr ""
"So let the king provide seed and fodder for those in the realm who work in "
"farming and raising cattle."

msgctxt "dn5:63.9"
msgid ""
"Ye bhoto rañño janapade ussahanti vāṇijjāya, tesaṃ bhavaṃ rājā pābhataṃ "
"anuppadetu."
msgstr "Let the king provide funding for those who work in trade."

msgctxt "dn5:63.10"
msgid ""
"Ye bhoto rañño janapade ussahanti rājaporise, tesaṃ bhavaṃ rājā "
"bhattavetanaṃ pakappetu."
msgstr "Let the king guarantee food and wages for those in government service."

msgctxt "dn5:63.11"
msgid "Te ca manussā sakammapasutā rañño janapadaṃ na viheṭhessanti;"
msgstr ""
"Then the people, occupied with their own work, will not harass the realm."

msgctxt "dn5:63.12"
msgid "mahā ca rañño rāsiko bhavissati."
msgstr "The king’s revenues will be great."

msgctxt "dn5:63.13"
msgid "Khemaṭṭhitā janapadā akaṇṭakā anuppīḷā."
msgstr ""
"When the country is secured as a sanctuary, free of being harried and "
"oppressed, the happy people, with joy in their hearts, dancing with children "
"at their breast, will dwell as if their houses were wide open.’"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "dn5:63.14"
msgid ""
"Manussā mudā modamānā ure putte naccentā apārutagharā maññe viharissantī’ti."
msgstr " "

msgctxt "dn5:63.15"
msgid ""
"‘Evaṃ, bho’ti kho, brāhmaṇa, rājā mahāvijito purohitassa brāhmaṇassa "
"paṭissutvā ye rañño janapade ussahiṃsu kasigorakkhe, tesaṃ rājā mahāvijito "
"bījabhattaṃ anuppadāsi."
msgstr ""
"The king agreed with the high priest’s advice and followed his "
"recommendation."

msgctxt "dn5:63.16"
msgid ""
"Ye ca rañño janapade ussahiṃsu vāṇijjāya, tesaṃ rājā mahāvijito pābhataṃ "
"anuppadāsi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:63.17"
msgid ""
"Ye ca rañño janapade ussahiṃsu rājaporise, tesaṃ rājā mahāvijito "
"bhattavetanaṃ pakappesi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:63.18"
msgid ""
"Te ca manussā sakammapasutā rañño janapadaṃ na viheṭhiṃsu, mahā ca rañño "
"rāsiko ahosi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:63.19"
msgid ""
"Khemaṭṭhitā janapadā akaṇṭakā anuppīḷā manussā mudā modamānā ure putte "
"naccentā apārutagharā maññe vihariṃsu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:63.20"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, brāhmaṇa, rājā mahāvijito purohitaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ āmantetvā etadavoca:"
msgstr "Then the king summoned the brahmin high priest and said to him:"

msgctxt "dn5:63.21"
msgid ""
"‘samūhato kho me bhoto dassukhīlo, bhoto saṃvidhānaṃ āgamma mahā ca me "
"rāsiko."
msgstr ""
"‘I have uprooted the barbarian obstacle. And relying on your plan my revenue "
"is now great."

msgctxt "dn5:63.22"
msgid ""
"Khemaṭṭhitā janapadā akaṇṭakā anuppīḷā manussā mudā modamānā ure putte "
"naccentā apārutagharā maññe viharanti."
msgstr ""
"Since the country is secured as a sanctuary, free of being harried and "
"oppressed, the happy people, with joy in their hearts, dancing with children "
"at their breast, dwell as if their houses were wide open."

msgctxt "dn5:63.23"
msgid "Icchāmahaṃ brāhmaṇa mahāyaññaṃ yajituṃ."
msgstr "Brahmin, I wish to perform a great sacrifice."

msgctxt "dn5:63.24"
msgid "Anusāsatu maṃ bhavaṃ yaṃ mama assa dīgharattaṃ hitāya sukhāyā’ti."
msgstr "Please instruct me. It will be for my lasting welfare and happiness.’"

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "dn5:64.1"
msgid "4.1. Catuparikkhāra"
msgstr "The Four Accessories"

#. </h3><p><a class="sc" id="58"></a><a class="wp" id="wp58"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts1.137"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:65.1"
msgid ""
"Tena hi bhavaṃ rājā ye bhoto rañño janapade khattiyā ānuyantā negamā ceva "
"jānapadā ca te bhavaṃ rājā āmantayataṃ:"
msgstr ""
"‘In that case, let the king announce this throughout the realm to the "
"aristocrat vassals,"

msgctxt "dn5:65.2"
msgid ""
"‘icchāmahaṃ, bho, mahāyaññaṃ yajituṃ, anujānantu me bhavanto yaṃ mama assa "
"dīgharattaṃ hitāya sukhāyā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:65.3"
msgid "Ye bhoto rañño janapade amaccā pārisajjā negamā ceva jānapadā ca …"
msgstr "ministers and counselors,"

msgctxt "dn5:65.4"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:65.5"
msgid "brāhmaṇamahāsālā negamā ceva jānapadā ca …"
msgstr "propertied brahmins,"

msgctxt "dn5:65.6"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:65.7"
msgid "gahapatinecayikā negamā ceva jānapadā ca, te bhavaṃ rājā āmantayataṃ:"
msgstr "and householders of substance, both of town and country:"

msgctxt "dn5:65.8"
msgid ""
"‘icchāmahaṃ, bho, mahāyaññaṃ yajituṃ, anujānantu me bhavanto yaṃ mama assa "
"dīgharattaṃ hitāya sukhāyā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I wish to perform a great sacrifice. Please grant your approval, gentlemen; "
"it will be for my lasting welfare and happiness.’"

msgctxt "dn5:65.9"
msgid ""
"‘Evaṃ, bho’ti kho, brāhmaṇa, rājā mahāvijito purohitassa brāhmaṇassa "
"paṭissutvā ye rañño janapade khattiyā ānuyantā negamā ceva jānapadā ca, te "
"rājā mahāvijito āmantesi:"
msgstr ""
"The king agreed with the high priest’s advice and followed his "
"recommendation."

msgctxt "dn5:65.10"
msgid ""
"‘icchāmahaṃ, bho, mahāyaññaṃ yajituṃ, anujānantu me bhavanto yaṃ mama assa "
"dīgharattaṃ hitāya sukhāyā’ti."
msgstr "And all of the people who were thus informed responded by saying:"

msgctxt "dn5:65.11"
msgid "‘Yajataṃ bhavaṃ rājā yaññaṃ, yaññakālo, mahārājā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘May the king perform a sacrifice! It is time for a sacrifice, Great King.’"

msgctxt "dn5:65.12"
msgid "Ye rañño janapade amaccā pārisajjā negamā ceva jānapadā ca …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:65.13"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:65.14"
msgid "brāhmaṇamahāsālā negamā ceva jānapadā ca …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:65.15"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:65.16"
msgid "gahapatinecayikā negamā ceva jānapadā ca, te rājā mahāvijito āmantesi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:65.17"
msgid "‘icchāmahaṃ, bho, mahāyaññaṃ yajituṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:65.18"
msgid "Anujānantu me bhavanto yaṃ mama assa dīgharattaṃ hitāya sukhāyā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:65.19"
msgid "‘Yajataṃ bhavaṃ rājā yaññaṃ, yaññakālo, mahārājā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:65.20"
msgid "Itime cattāro anumatipakkhā tasseva yaññassa parikkhārā bhavanti."
msgstr ""
"And so these four consenting factions became accessories to the sacrifice."

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "dn5:66.1"
msgid "4.2. Aṭṭhaparikkhāra"
msgstr "The Eight Accessories"

#. </h3><p><a class="sc" id="59"></a><a class="wp" id="wp59"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:67.1"
msgid "Rājā mahāvijito aṭṭhahaṅgehi samannāgato—"
msgstr "King Mahāvijita possessed eight factors."

msgctxt "dn5:67.2"
msgid ""
"ubhato sujāto mātito ca pitito ca saṃsuddhagahaṇiko yāva sattamā "
"pitāmahayugā akkhitto anupakkuṭṭho jātivādena;"
msgstr ""
"He was well born on both his mother’s and father’s side, of pure descent, "
"irrefutable and impeccable in questions of ancestry back to the seventh "
"paternal generation."

msgctxt "dn5:67.3"
msgid ""
"abhirūpo dassanīyo pāsādiko paramāya vaṇṇapokkharatāya samannāgato "
"brahmavaṇṇī brahmavacchasī akhuddāvakāso dassanāya;"
msgstr ""
"He was attractive, good-looking, lovely, of surpassing beauty. He was "
"magnificent, splendid, remarkable to behold."

msgctxt "dn5:67.4"
msgid ""
"aḍḍho mahaddhano mahābhogo pahūtajātarūparajato pahūtavittūpakaraṇo "
"pahūtadhanadhañño paripuṇṇakosakoṭṭhāgāro;"
msgstr ""
"He was rich, affluent, and wealthy, with lots of gold and silver, lots of "
"property and assets, lots of money and grain, and a full treasury and "
"storehouses."

# Here sahati is the preferred reading, against PTS, RD, MW. This sounds rather like Alexander arriving in India. 
#. VAR: sahati → patapati (bj, pts1) | tapati (s1-3)
msgctxt "dn5:67.5"
msgid ""
"balavā caturaṅginiyā senāya samannāgato assavāya ovādapaṭikarāya sahati "
"maññe paccatthike yasasā;"
msgstr ""
"He was powerful, having an army of four divisions that was obedient and "
"carried out instructions. He’d probably beat his enemies just with his "
"reputation."

# For this long compound, see SN 2.23
msgctxt "dn5:67.6"
msgid ""
"saddho dāyako dānapati anāvaṭadvāro "
"samaṇabrāhmaṇakapaṇaddhikavaṇibbakayācakānaṃ opānabhūto puññāni karoti;"
msgstr ""
"He was faithful, generous, a donor, his door always open. He was a well-"
"spring of support, making merit with ascetics and brahmins, for paupers, "
"vagrants, travelers, and beggars."

msgctxt "dn5:67.7"
msgid ""
"bahussuto tassa tassa sutajātassa, tassa tasseva kho pana bhāsitassa atthaṃ "
"jānāti:"
msgstr ""
"He was very learned in diverse fields of learning. He understood the meaning "
"of diverse statements, saying:"

msgctxt "dn5:67.8"
msgid "‘ayaṃ imassa bhāsitassa attho ayaṃ imassa bhāsitassa attho’ti;"
msgstr "‘This is what that statement means; that is what this statement means.’"

msgctxt "dn5:67.9"
msgid ""
"paṇḍito, viyatto, medhāvī, paṭibalo, atītānāgatapaccuppanne atthe cintetuṃ."
msgstr ""
"He was astute, competent, and intelligent, able to think issues through as "
"they bear upon the past, future, and present. "

msgctxt "dn5:67.10"
msgid "Rājā mahāvijito imehi aṭṭhahaṅgehi samannāgato."
msgstr "These are the eight factors that King Mahāvijita possessed."

msgctxt "dn5:67.11"
msgid "Iti imānipi aṭṭhaṅgāni tasseva yaññassa parikkhārā bhavanti."
msgstr "And so these eight factors also became accessories to the sacrifice."

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "dn5:68.1"
msgid "4.3. Catuparikkhāra"
msgstr "Four More Accessories"

#. </h3><p><a class="sc" id="60"></a><a class="wp" id="wp60"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts1.138"></a>
#. VAR: Purohito → purohitopi (bj, km, c1)
msgctxt "dn5:69.1"
msgid ""
"Purohito brāhmaṇo catūhaṅgehi samannāgato, ubhato sujāto mātito ca pitito ca "
"saṃsuddhagahaṇiko yāva sattamā pitāmahayugā akkhitto anupakkuṭṭho jātivādena;"
msgstr ""
"And the brahmin high priest had four factors. He was well born on both his "
"mother’s and father’s side, of pure descent, irrefutable and impeccable in "
"questions of ancestry back to the seventh paternal generation."

msgctxt "dn5:69.2"
msgid ""
"ajjhāyako mantadharo tiṇṇaṃ vedānaṃ pāragū sanighaṇḍukeṭubhānaṃ "
"sākkharappabhedānaṃ itihāsapañcamānaṃ padako veyyākaraṇo "
"lokāyatamahāpurisalakkhaṇesu anavayo;"
msgstr ""
"He recited and remembered the hymns, and was an expert in the three Vedas, "
"together with their vocabularies, ritual, phonology and etymology, and the "
"testament as fifth. He knew philology and grammar, and was well versed in "
"cosmology and the marks of a great man."

msgctxt "dn5:69.3"
msgid "sīlavā vuddhasīlī vuddhasīlena samannāgato;"
msgstr "He was ethical, mature in ethical conduct."

msgctxt "dn5:69.4"
msgid "paṇḍito viyatto medhāvī paṭhamo vā dutiyo vā sujaṃ paggaṇhantānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"He was astute and clever, being the first or second to hold the sacrificial "
"ladle."

msgctxt "dn5:69.5"
msgid "Purohito brāhmaṇo imehi catūhaṅgehi samannāgato."
msgstr "These are the four factors that the brahmin high priest possessed."

#. VAR: imānipi → imāni (c1)
msgctxt "dn5:69.6"
msgid "Iti imānipi cattāri aṅgāni tasseva yaññassa parikkhārā bhavanti."
msgstr "And so these four factors also became accessories to the sacrifice."

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "dn5:70.1"
msgid "4.4. Tissovidhā"
msgstr "The Three Modes"

#. </h3><p><a class="sc" id="61"></a><a class="wp" id="wp61"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:71.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, brāhmaṇa, purohito brāhmaṇo rañño mahāvijitassa pubbeva yaññā "
"tisso vidhā desesi."
msgstr ""
"Next, before the sacrifice, the brahmin high priest taught the three modes "
"to the king."

#. VAR: yiṭṭhukāmassa → yajamānassa (s1-3) | yiṭṭhakāmassa (mr)
msgctxt "dn5:71.2"
msgid ""
"Siyā kho pana bhoto rañño mahāyaññaṃ yiṭṭhukāmassa kocideva vippaṭisāro:"
msgstr ""
"‘Now, though the king wants to perform a great sacrifice, he might have "
"certain regrets, thinking:"

msgctxt "dn5:71.3"
msgid ""
"‘“mahā vata me bhogakkhandho vigacchissatī”ti, so bhotā raññā vippaṭisāro na "
"karaṇīyo."
msgstr "“I shall lose a great fortune,” or "

msgctxt "dn5:71.4"
msgid "Siyā kho pana bhoto rañño mahāyaññaṃ yajamānassa kocideva vippaṭisāro:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:71.5"
msgid ""
"“mahā vata me bhogakkhandho vigacchatī”ti, so bhotā raññā vippaṭisāro na "
"karaṇīyo."
msgstr "“I am losing a great fortune,” or "

msgctxt "dn5:71.6"
msgid "Siyā kho pana bhoto rañño mahāyaññaṃ yiṭṭhassa kocideva vippaṭisāro:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:71.7"
msgid ""
"“mahā vata me bhogakkhandho vigato”ti, so bhotā raññā vippaṭisāro na "
"karaṇīyo’ti."
msgstr ""
"“I have lost a great fortune.” But the king should not harbor such regrets."

msgctxt "dn5:71.8"
msgid ""
"Imā kho, brāhmaṇa, purohito brāhmaṇo rañño mahāvijitassa pubbeva yaññā tisso "
"vidhā desesi."
msgstr ""
"These are the three modes that the brahmin high priest taught to the king "
"before the sacrifice."

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "dn5:72.1"
msgid "4.5. Dasaākāra"
msgstr "The Ten Respects"

#. </h3><p><a class="sc" id="62"></a><a class="wp" id="wp62"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts1.139"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:73.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, brāhmaṇa, purohito brāhmaṇo rañño mahāvijitassa pubbeva yaññā "
"dasahākārehi paṭiggāhakesu vippaṭisāraṃ paṭivinesi."
msgstr ""
"Next, before the sacrifice, the brahmin high priest dispelled the king’s "
"regret regarding the recipients in ten respects."

msgctxt "dn5:73.2"
msgid "‘Āgamissanti kho bhoto yaññaṃ pāṇātipātinopi pāṇātipātā paṭiviratāpi."
msgstr ""
"‘There will come to the sacrifice those who kill living creatures and those "
"who refrain from killing living creatures."

msgctxt "dn5:73.3"
msgid "Ye tattha pāṇātipātino, tesaññeva tena."
msgstr ""
"As to those who kill living creatures, the outcome of that is theirs alone."

# PTS, followed by RD and MW, acknowledges sajjata only as vl, but it is in comm, so should be accepted.
msgctxt "dn5:73.4"
msgid ""
"Ye tattha pāṇātipātā paṭiviratā, te ārabbha yajataṃ bhavaṃ, sajjataṃ bhavaṃ, "
"modataṃ bhavaṃ, cittameva bhavaṃ antaraṃ pasādetu."
msgstr ""
"But as to those who refrain from killing living creatures, it is for their "
"sakes that the king should sacrifice, relinquish, rejoice, and gain "
"confidence in his heart."

msgctxt "dn5:73.5"
msgid "Āgamissanti kho bhoto yaññaṃ adinnādāyinopi adinnādānā paṭiviratāpi …"
msgstr "There will come to the sacrifice those who steal …"

msgctxt "dn5:73.6"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:73.7"
msgid "kāmesu micchācārinopi kāmesumicchācārā paṭiviratāpi …"
msgstr "commit sexual misconduct …"

msgctxt "dn5:73.8"
msgid "musāvādinopi musāvādā paṭiviratāpi …"
msgstr "lie …"

msgctxt "dn5:73.9"
msgid "pisuṇavācinopi pisuṇāya vācāya paṭiviratāpi …"
msgstr "use divisive speech …"

msgctxt "dn5:73.10"
msgid "pharusavācinopi pharusāya vācāya paṭiviratāpi …"
msgstr "use harsh speech …"

msgctxt "dn5:73.11"
msgid "samphappalāpinopi samphappalāpā paṭiviratāpi …"
msgstr "use nonsensical speech …"

msgctxt "dn5:73.12"
msgid "abhijjhālunopi anabhijjhālunopi …"
msgstr "are covetous …"

msgctxt "dn5:73.13"
msgid "byāpannacittāpi abyāpannacittāpi …"
msgstr "have ill will …"

msgctxt "dn5:73.14"
msgid "micchādiṭṭhikāpi sammādiṭṭhikāpi …."
msgstr "have wrong view and those who have right view."

msgctxt "dn5:73.15"
msgid "Ye tattha micchādiṭṭhikā, tesaññeva tena."
msgstr "As to those who have wrong view, the outcome of that is theirs alone."

msgctxt "dn5:73.16"
msgid ""
"Ye tattha sammādiṭṭhikā, te ārabbha yajataṃ bhavaṃ, sajjataṃ bhavaṃ, modataṃ "
"bhavaṃ, cittameva bhavaṃ antaraṃ pasādetū’ti."
msgstr ""
"But as to those who have right view, it is for their sakes that the king "
"should sacrifice, relinquish, rejoice, and gain confidence in his heart.’"

msgctxt "dn5:73.17"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, brāhmaṇa, purohito brāhmaṇo rañño mahāvijitassa pubbeva yaññā "
"dasahākārehi paṭiggāhakesu vippaṭisāraṃ paṭivinesi."
msgstr ""
"These are the ten respects in which the high priest dispelled the king’s "
"regret regarding the recipients before the sacrifice."

