#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="69"></a><a class="wp" id="wp69"></a>
#. VAR: barihisatthāya → pari­hiṃ­satthāya (si, s1-3, mr) | para­hiṃ­satthāya
#. (mr)
msgctxt "dn5:81.1"
msgid ""
"Tasmiṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, yaññe neva gāvo haññiṃsu, na ajeḷakā haññiṃsu, na "
"kukkuṭasūkarā haññiṃsu, na vividhā pāṇā saṅghātaṃ āpajjiṃsu, na rukkhā "
"chijjiṃsu yūpatthāya, na dabbhā lūyiṃsu barihisatthāya."
msgstr ""
"And brahmin, in that sacrifice no cattle were killed, no goats were killed, "
"and no chickens or pigs were killed. There was no slaughter of various kinds "
"of creatures. No trees were felled for the sacrificial post. No grass was "
"reaped to strew over the place of sacrifice."

msgctxt "dn5:81.2"
msgid ""
"Yepissa ahesuṃ dāsāti vā pessāti vā kammakarāti vā, tepi na daṇḍatajjitā na "
"bhayatajjitā na assumukhā rudamānā parikammāni akaṃsu."
msgstr ""
"No bondservants, employees, or workers did their jobs under threat of "
"punishment and danger, weeping with tearful faces."

msgctxt "dn5:81.3"
msgid "Atha kho ye icchiṃsu, te akaṃsu, ye na icchiṃsu, na te akaṃsu;"
msgstr ""
"Those who wished to work did so, while those who did not wish to did not."

msgctxt "dn5:81.4"
msgid "yaṃ icchiṃsu, taṃ akaṃsu, yaṃ na icchiṃsu, na taṃ akaṃsu."
msgstr ""
"They did the work they wanted to, and did not do what they didn’t want to."

msgctxt "dn5:81.5"
msgid "Sappitelanavanītadadhimadhuphāṇitena ceva so yañño niṭṭhānamagamāsi."
msgstr ""
"The sacrifice was completed with just ghee, oil, butter, curds, honey, and "
"molasses."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="70"></a><a class="wp" id="wp70"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts1.142"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:82.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, brāhmaṇa, khattiyā ānuyantā negamā ceva jānapadā ca, amaccā "
"pārisajjā negamā ceva jānapadā ca, brāhmaṇamahāsālā negamā ceva jānapadā ca, "
"gahapatinecayikā negamā ceva jānapadā ca pahūtaṃ sāpateyyaṃ ādāya rājānaṃ "
"mahāvijitaṃ upasaṅkamitvā evamāhaṃsu:"
msgstr ""
"Then the aristocrat vassals, propertied brahmins, and householders of "
"substance of both town and country came to the king bringing abundant wealth "
"and said:"

# RD's translation of this passage is more accurate than MW's.
msgctxt "dn5:82.2"
msgid ""
"‘idaṃ, deva, pahūtaṃ sāpateyyaṃ devaññeva uddissābhataṃ, taṃ devo "
"paṭiggaṇhātū’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Sire, this abundant wealth is specially for you alone; may Your Highness "
"accept it!’"

msgctxt "dn5:82.3"
msgid ""
"‘Alaṃ, bho, mamāpidaṃ pahūtaṃ sāpateyyaṃ dhammikena balinā abhisaṅkhataṃ;"
msgstr ""
"‘There’s enough raised for me through regular taxes. Let this be for you; "
"and here, take even more!’"

msgctxt "dn5:82.4"
msgid "tañca vo hotu, ito ca bhiyyo harathā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:82.5"
msgid "Te raññā paṭikkhittā ekamantaṃ apakkamma evaṃ samacintesuṃ:"
msgstr ""
"When the king turned them down, they withdrew to one side to think up a plan:"

msgctxt "dn5:82.6"
msgid ""
"‘na kho etaṃ amhākaṃ patirūpaṃ, yaṃ mayaṃ imāni sāpateyyāni punadeva sakāni "
"gharāni paṭihareyyāma."
msgstr ""
"‘It wouldn’t be proper for us to take this abundant wealth back to our own "
"homes."

msgctxt "dn5:82.7"
msgid ""
"Rājā kho mahāvijito mahāyaññaṃ yajati, handassa mayaṃ anuyāgino homā’ti."
msgstr ""
"King Mahāvijita is performing a great sacrifice. Let us make an offering as "
"an auxiliary sacrifice.’"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="71"></a><a class="wp" id="wp71"></a>
#. VAR: yaññavāṭassa → yaññāvāṭassa (bj, pts1, mr) | yaññavātassa (s1-3)
msgctxt "dn5:83.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, brāhmaṇa, puratthimena yaññavāṭassa khattiyā ānuyantā negamā ceva "
"jānapadā ca dānāni paṭṭhapesuṃ."
msgstr ""
"Then the aristocrat vassals of town and country set up gifts to the east of "
"the sacrificial pit."

msgctxt "dn5:83.2"
msgid ""
"Dakkhiṇena yaññavāṭassa amaccā pārisajjā negamā ceva jānapadā ca dānāni "
"paṭṭhapesuṃ."
msgstr ""
"The ministers and counselors of town and country set up gifts to the south "
"of the sacrificial pit."

msgctxt "dn5:83.3"
msgid ""
"Pacchimena yaññavāṭassa brāhmaṇamahāsālā negamā ceva jānapadā ca dānāni "
"paṭṭhapesuṃ."
msgstr ""
"The propertied brahmins of town and country set up gifts to the west of the "
"sacrificial pit."

msgctxt "dn5:83.4"
msgid ""
"Uttarena yaññavāṭassa gahapatinecayikā negamā ceva jānapadā ca dānāni "
"paṭṭhapesuṃ."
msgstr ""
"The householders of substance of town and country set up gifts to the north "
"of the sacrificial pit."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="72"></a><a class="wp" id="wp72"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:84.1"
msgid ""
"Tesupi kho, brāhmaṇa, yaññesu neva gāvo haññiṃsu, na ajeḷakā haññiṃsu, na "
"kukkuṭasūkarā haññiṃsu, na vividhā pāṇā saṅghātaṃ āpajjiṃsu, na rukkhā "
"chijjiṃsu yūpatthāya, na dabbhā lūyiṃsu barihisatthāya."
msgstr ""
"And brahmin, in that sacrifice too no cattle were killed, no goats were "
"killed, and no chickens or pigs were killed. There was no slaughter of "
"various kinds of creatures. No trees were felled for the sacrificial post. "
"No grass was reaped to strew over the place of sacrifice."

msgctxt "dn5:84.2"
msgid ""
"Yepi nesaṃ ahesuṃ dāsāti vā pessāti vā kammakarāti vā, tepi na daṇḍatajjitā "
"na bhayatajjitā na assumukhā rudamānā parikammāni akaṃsu."
msgstr ""
"No bondservants, employees, or workers did their jobs under threat of "
"punishment and danger, weeping with tearful faces."

msgctxt "dn5:84.3"
msgid "Atha kho ye icchiṃsu, te akaṃsu, ye na icchiṃsu, na te akaṃsu;"
msgstr ""
"Those who wished to work did so, while those who did not wish to did not."

msgctxt "dn5:84.4"
msgid "yaṃ icchiṃsu, taṃ akaṃsu, yaṃ na icchiṃsu na taṃ akaṃsu."
msgstr ""
"They did the work they wanted to, and did not do what they didn’t want to."

msgctxt "dn5:84.5"
msgid "Sappitelanavanītadadhimadhuphāṇitena ceva te yaññā niṭṭhānamagamaṃsu."
msgstr ""
"The sacrifice was completed with just ghee, oil, butter, curds, honey, and "
"molasses."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="73"></a><a class="wp" id="wp73"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts1.143"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:85.1"
msgid ""
"Iti cattāro ca anumatipakkhā, rājā mahāvijito aṭṭhahaṅgehi samannāgato, "
"purohito brāhmaṇo catūhaṅgehi samannāgato;"
msgstr ""
"And so there were four consenting factions, eight factors possessed by king "
"Mahāvijita, four factors possessed by the high priest,"

msgctxt "dn5:85.2"
msgid "tisso ca vidhā."
msgstr "and three modes."

msgctxt "dn5:85.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, brāhmaṇa, tividhā yaññasampadā soḷasaparikkhārā”ti."
msgstr ""
"Brahmin, this is called the sacrifice accomplished with three modes and "
"sixteen accessories.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="74"></a><a class="wp" id="wp74"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:86.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, te brāhmaṇā unnādino uccāsaddamahāsaddā ahesuṃ:"
msgstr "When he said this, those brahmins made an uproar:"

msgctxt "dn5:86.2"
msgid "“aho yañño, aho yaññasampadā”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Hooray for such sacrifice! Hooray for the accomplishment of such sacrifice!”"
"  "

msgctxt "dn5:86.3"
msgid "Kūṭadanto pana brāhmaṇo tūṇhībhūtova nisinno hoti."
msgstr "But the brahmin Kūṭadanta sat in silence."

msgctxt "dn5:86.4"
msgid "Atha kho te brāhmaṇā kūṭadantaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ etadavocuṃ:"
msgstr "So those brahmins said to him:"

msgctxt "dn5:86.5"
msgid ""
"“kasmā pana bhavaṃ kūṭadanto samaṇassa gotamassa subhāsitaṃ subhāsitato "
"nābbhanumodatī”ti?"
msgstr "“How can you not applaud the ascetic Gotama’s fine words?”"

msgctxt "dn5:86.6"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bho, samaṇassa gotamassa subhāsitaṃ subhāsitato nābbhanumodāmi."
msgstr "“It’s not that I don’t applaud what he said."

msgctxt "dn5:86.7"
msgid ""
"Muddhāpi tassa vipateyya, yo samaṇassa gotamassa subhāsitaṃ subhāsitato "
"nābbhanumodeyya."
msgstr "If anyone didn’t applaud such fine words, their head would explode!"

msgctxt "dn5:86.8"
msgid "Api ca me, bho, evaṃ hoti—"
msgstr "But, gentlemen, it occurs to me that"

msgctxt "dn5:86.9"
msgid "samaṇo gotamo na evamāha:"
msgstr "the ascetic Gotama does not say:"

msgctxt "dn5:86.10"
msgid "‘evaṃ me sutan’ti vā ‘evaṃ arahati bhavitun’ti vā;"
msgstr "‘So I have heard’ or ‘It ought to be like this.’"

msgctxt "dn5:86.11"
msgid "api ca samaṇo gotamo:"
msgstr "Rather, he just says:"

msgctxt "dn5:86.12"
msgid "‘evaṃ tadā āsi, itthaṃ tadā āsi’ tveva bhāsati."
msgstr "‘So it was then, this is how it was then.’"

msgctxt "dn5:86.13"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ bho evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "It occurs to me that"

msgctxt "dn5:86.14"
msgid ""
"‘addhā samaṇo gotamo tena samayena rājā vā ahosi mahāvijito yaññassāmi "
"purohito vā brāhmaṇo tassa yaññassa yājetā’ti."
msgstr ""
"the ascetic Gotama at that time must have been King Mahāvijita, the owner of "
"the sacrifice, or else the brahmin high priest who facilitated the sacrifice "
"for him."

msgctxt "dn5:86.15"
msgid ""
"Abhijānāti pana bhavaṃ gotamo evarūpaṃ yaññaṃ yajitvā vā yājetvā vā kāyassa "
"bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjitā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"Does Master Gotama recall having performed such a sacrifice, or having "
"facilitated it, and then, when his body broke up, after death, being reborn "
"in a good place, a heavenly realm?”"

msgctxt "dn5:86.16"
msgid ""
"“Abhijānāmahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, evarūpaṃ yaññaṃ yajitvā vā yājetvā vā kāyassa "
"bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjitā, ahaṃ tena samayena "
"purohito brāhmaṇo ahosiṃ tassa yaññassa yājetā”ti."
msgstr ""
"“I do recall that, brahmin. For at that time I was the brahmin high priest "
"who facilitated the sacrifice.”"

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn5:87.1"
msgid "5. Niccadānaanukulayañña"
msgstr "A Regular Gift as an Ongoing Family Sacrifice."

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="75"></a><a class="wp" id="wp75"></a>
#. VAR: appaṭṭhataro → appatthataro (s1-3, km)
#. VAR: tividhāya yaññasampadāya → tividha­yañña­sam­padāya (mr)
msgctxt "dn5:88.1"
msgid ""
"“Atthi pana, bho gotama, añño yañño imāya tividhāya yaññasampadāya "
"soḷasaparikkhārāya appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca "
"mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“But Master Gotama, apart from that sacrifice accomplished with three modes "
"and sixteen accessories, is there any other sacrifice that has fewer "
"requirements and undertakings, yet is more fruitful and beneficial?”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="76"></a><a class="wp" id="wp76"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts1.144"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:89.1"
msgid ""
"“Atthi kho, brāhmaṇa, añño yañño imāya tividhāya yaññasampadāya "
"soḷasaparikkhārāya appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca "
"mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti."
msgstr "“There is, brahmin.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="77"></a><a class="wp" id="wp77"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:90.1"
msgid ""
"“Katamo pana so, bho gotama, yañño imāya tividhāya yaññasampadāya "
"soḷasaparikkhārāya appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca "
"mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti?"
msgstr "“But what is it?”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="78"></a><a class="wp" id="wp78"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:91.1"
msgid ""
"“Yāni kho pana tāni, brāhmaṇa, niccadānāni anukulayaññāni sīlavante "
"pabbajite uddissa diyyanti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:91.2"
msgid ""
"ayaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, yañño imāya tividhāya yaññasampadāya soḷasaparikkhārāya "
"appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro "
"cā”ti."
msgstr ""
"This sacrifice has fewer requirements and undertakings, yet is more fruitful "
"and beneficial.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="79"></a><a class="wp" id="wp79"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:92.1"
msgid ""
"“Ko nu kho, bho gotama, hetu ko paccayo, yena taṃ niccadānaṃ anukulayaññaṃ "
"imāya tividhāya yaññasampadāya soḷasaparikkhārāya appaṭṭhatarañca "
"appasamārambhatarañca mahapphalatarañca mahānisaṃsatarañcā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“What is the cause, Master Gotama, what is the reason why those regular "
"gifts as ongoing family sacrifice have fewer requirements and undertakings, "
"yet are more fruitful and beneficial, compared with the sacrifice "
"accomplished with three modes and sixteen accessories?”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="80"></a><a class="wp" id="wp80"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:93.1"
msgid ""
"“Na kho, brāhmaṇa, evarūpaṃ yaññaṃ upasaṅkamanti arahanto vā arahattamaggaṃ "
"vā samāpannā."
msgstr ""
"“Because neither perfected ones nor those who have entered the path to "
"perfection will attend such a sacrifice."

msgctxt "dn5:93.2"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "dn5:93.3"
msgid ""
"Dissanti hettha, brāhmaṇa, daṇḍappahārāpi galaggahāpi, tasmā evarūpaṃ yaññaṃ "
"na upasaṅkamanti arahanto vā arahattamaggaṃ vā samāpannā."
msgstr "Because beatings and throttlings are seen there."

msgctxt "dn5:93.4"
msgid ""
"Yāni kho pana tāni, brāhmaṇa, niccadānāni anukulayaññāni sīlavante pabbajite "
"uddissa diyyanti;"
msgstr ""
"But the regular gifts as ongoing family sacrifice given specially to ethical "
"renunciates;"

msgctxt "dn5:93.5"
msgid ""
"evarūpaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, yaññaṃ upasaṅkamanti arahanto vā arahattamaggaṃ vā "
"samāpannā."
msgstr ""
"perfected ones and those who have entered the path to perfection will attend "
"such a sacrifice."

msgctxt "dn5:93.6"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "dn5:93.7"
msgid ""
"Na hettha, brāhmaṇa, dissanti daṇḍappahārāpi galaggahāpi, tasmā evarūpaṃ "
"yaññaṃ upasaṅkamanti arahanto vā arahattamaggaṃ vā samāpannā."
msgstr "Because no beatings and throttlings are seen there."

msgctxt "dn5:93.8"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, hetu ayaṃ paccayo, yena taṃ niccadānaṃ anukulayaññaṃ "
"imāya tividhāya yaññasampadāya soḷasaparikkhārāya appaṭṭhatarañca "
"appasamārambhatarañca mahapphalatarañca mahānisaṃsatarañcā”ti."
msgstr ""
"This is the cause, brahmin, this is the reason why those regular gifts as "
"ongoing family sacrifice have fewer requirements and undertakings, yet are "
"more fruitful and beneficial, compared with the sacrifice accomplished with "
"three modes and sixteen accessories.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="81"></a><a class="wp" id="wp81"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts1.145"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:94.1"
msgid ""
"“Atthi pana, bho gotama, añño yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya "
"soḷasaparikkhārāya iminā ca niccadānena anukulayaññena appaṭṭhataro ca "
"appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“But Master Gotama, apart from that sacrifice accomplished with three modes "
"and sixteen accessories and those regular gifts as ongoing family sacrifice, "
"is there any other sacrifice that has fewer requirements and undertakings, "
"yet is more fruitful and beneficial?”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="82"></a><a class="wp" id="wp82"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:95.1"
msgid ""
"“Atthi kho, brāhmaṇa, añño yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya "
"soḷasaparikkhārāya iminā ca niccadānena anukulayaññena appaṭṭhataro ca "
"appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti."
msgstr "“There is, brahmin.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="83"></a><a class="wp" id="wp83"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:96.1"
msgid ""
"“Katamo pana so, bho gotama, yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya "
"soḷasaparikkhārāya iminā ca niccadānena anukulayaññena appaṭṭhataro ca "
"appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti?"
msgstr "“But what is it?”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="84"></a><a class="wp" id="wp84"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:97.1"
msgid ""
"“Yo kho, brāhmaṇa, cātuddisaṃ saṅghaṃ uddissa vihāraṃ karoti, ayaṃ kho, "
"brāhmaṇa, yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya soḷasaparikkhārāya iminā "
"ca niccadānena anukulayaññena appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca "
"mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti."
msgstr ""
"“When someone gives a dwelling specially for the Saṅgha of the four "
"quarters.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="85"></a><a class="wp" id="wp85"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:98.1"
msgid ""
"“Atthi pana, bho gotama, añño yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya "
"soḷasaparikkhārāya iminā ca niccadānena anukulayaññena iminā ca vihāradānena "
"appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro "
"cā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“But is there any other sacrifice that has fewer requirements and "
"undertakings, yet is more fruitful and beneficial?”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="86"></a><a class="wp" id="wp86"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:99.1"
msgid ""
"“Atthi kho, brāhmaṇa, añño yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya "
"soḷasaparikkhārāya iminā ca niccadānena anukulayaññena iminā ca vihāradānena "
"appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro "
"cā”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="87"></a><a class="wp" id="wp87"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:100.1"
msgid ""
"“Katamo pana so, bho gotama, yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya "
"soḷasaparikkhārāya iminā ca niccadānena anukulayaññena iminā ca vihāradānena "
"appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro "
"cā”ti?"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="88"></a><a class="wp" id="wp88"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts1.146"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:101.1"
msgid ""
"“Yo kho, brāhmaṇa, pasannacitto buddhaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchati, dhammaṃ saraṇaṃ "
"gacchati, saṅghaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchati;"
msgstr ""
"“When someone with confident heart goes for refuge to the Buddha, the "
"teaching, and the Saṅgha.”"

msgctxt "dn5:101.2"
msgid ""
"ayaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya "
"soḷasaparikkhārāya iminā ca niccadānena anukulayaññena iminā ca vihāradānena "
"appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro "
"cā”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="89"></a><a class="wp" id="wp89"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:102.1"
msgid ""
"“Atthi pana, bho gotama, añño yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya "
"soḷasaparikkhārāya iminā ca niccadānena anukulayaññena iminā ca vihāradānena "
"imehi ca saraṇagamanehi appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro "
"ca mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“But is there any other sacrifice that has fewer requirements and "
"undertakings, yet is more fruitful and beneficial?”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="90"></a><a class="wp" id="wp90"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:103.1"
msgid ""
"“Atthi kho, brāhmaṇa, añño yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya "
"soḷasaparikkhārāya iminā ca niccadānena anukulayaññena iminā ca vihāradānena "
"imehi ca saraṇagamanehi appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro "
"ca mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="91"></a><a class="wp" id="wp91"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:104.1"
msgid ""
"“Katamo pana so, bho gotama, yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya "
"soḷasaparikkhārāya iminā ca niccadānena anukulayaññena iminā ca vihāradānena "
"imehi ca saraṇagamanehi appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro "
"ca mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti?"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="92"></a><a class="wp" id="wp92"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:105.1"
msgid "“Yo kho, brāhmaṇa, pasannacitto sikkhāpadāni samādiyati—"
msgstr "“When someone with a confident heart undertakes the training rules"

msgctxt "dn5:105.2"
msgid ""
"pāṇātipātā veramaṇiṃ, adinnādānā veramaṇiṃ, kāmesumicchācārā veramaṇiṃ, "
"musāvādā veramaṇiṃ, surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā veramaṇiṃ."
msgstr ""
"to refrain from killing living creatures, stealing, sexual misconduct, "
"lying, and alcohol and drugs, which cause negligence.”"

msgctxt "dn5:105.3"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya "
"soḷasaparikkhārāya iminā ca niccadānena anukulayaññena iminā ca vihāradānena "
"imehi ca saraṇagamanehi appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro "
"ca mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="93"></a><a class="wp" id="wp93"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:106.1"
msgid ""
"“Atthi pana, bho gotama, añño yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya "
"soḷasaparikkhārāya iminā ca niccadānena anukulayaññena iminā ca vihāradānena "
"imehi ca saraṇagamanehi imehi ca sikkhāpadehi appaṭṭhataro ca "
"appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“But is there any other sacrifice that has fewer requirements and "
"undertakings, yet is more fruitful and beneficial?”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="94"></a><a class="wp" id="wp94"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:107.1"
msgid ""
"“Atthi kho, brāhmaṇa, añño yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya "
