msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn5:109.3"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, bhikkhu sīlasampanno hoti …"
msgstr "That’s how a mendicant is accomplished in ethics. …"

msgctxt "dn5:109.4"
msgid "pe …"
