"and finer than this.”"

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn5:111.1"
msgid "6. Kūṭadantaupāsakattapaṭivedanā"
msgstr "Kūṭadanta Declares Himself a Lay Follower"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="98"></a><a class="wp" id="wp98"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts1.148"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:112.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, kūṭadanto brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he had spoken, Kūṭadanta said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "dn5:112.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama, abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama."
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama! Excellent!"

msgctxt "dn5:112.3"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bho gotama, nikkujjitaṃ vā ukkujjeyya, paṭicchannaṃ vā "
"vivareyya, mūḷhassa vā maggaṃ ācikkheyya, andhakāre vā telapajjotaṃ dhāreyya:"
msgstr ""
"As if he was righting the overturned, or revealing the hidden, or pointing "
"out the path to the lost, or lighting a lamp in the dark  "

msgctxt "dn5:112.4"
msgid "‘cakkhumanto rūpāni dakkhantī’ti;"
msgstr "so people with good eyes can see what’s there,  "

msgctxt "dn5:112.5"
msgid "evamevaṃ bhotā gotamena anekapariyāyena dhammo pakāsito."
msgstr "just so have you made the Teaching clear in many ways."

msgctxt "dn5:112.6"
msgid "Esāhaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchāmi dhammañca bhikkhusaṅghañca."
msgstr ""
"I go for refuge to Master Gotama, to the Dharma, and to the mendicant Saṅgha."

msgctxt "dn5:112.7"
msgid "Upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gataṃ."
msgstr ""
"From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has "
"gone for refuge for life."

msgctxt "dn5:112.8"
msgid ""
"Esāhaṃ, bho gotama, satta ca usabhasatāni satta ca vacchatarasatāni satta ca "
"vacchatarīsatāni satta ca ajasatāni satta ca urabbhasatāni muñcāmi, jīvitaṃ "
"demi, haritāni ceva tiṇāni khādantu, sītāni ca pānīyāni pivantu, sīto ca "
"nesaṃ vāto upavāyatū”ti."
msgstr ""
"And these bulls, bullocks, heifers, goats and rams—seven hundred of each—I "
"release them, I grant them life! Let them eat green grass and drink cool "
"water, and may a cool breeze blow upon them!”"

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn5:113.1"
msgid "7. Sotāpattiphalasacchikiriyā"
msgstr "The Realization of the Fruit of Stream-Entry"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="99"></a><a class="wp" id="wp99"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:114.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā kūṭadantassa brāhmaṇassa anupubbiṃ kathaṃ kathesi, "
"seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "Then the Buddha taught Kūṭadanta step by step, with"

msgctxt "dn5:114.2"
msgid "dānakathaṃ sīlakathaṃ saggakathaṃ;"
msgstr "talk on giving, ethical conduct, and heaven."

msgctxt "dn5:114.3"
msgid "kāmānaṃ ādīnavaṃ okāraṃ saṅkilesaṃ nekkhamme ānisaṃsaṃ pakāsesi."
msgstr ""
"He explained the drawbacks of sensual pleasures, so sordid and corrupt, and "
"the benefit of renunciation. "

msgctxt "dn5:114.4"
msgid ""
"Yadā bhagavā aññāsi kūṭadantaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ kallacittaṃ muducittaṃ "
"vinīvaraṇacittaṃ udaggacittaṃ pasannacittaṃ, atha yā buddhānaṃ sāmukkaṃsikā "
"dhammadesanā, taṃ pakāsesi—"
msgstr ""
"And when he knew that Kūṭadanta’s mind was ready, pliable, rid of "
"hindrances, joyful, and confident he explained the special teaching of the "
"Buddhas:"

msgctxt "dn5:114.5"
msgid "dukkhaṃ samudayaṃ nirodhaṃ maggaṃ."
msgstr "suffering, its origin, its cessation, and the path."

msgctxt "dn5:114.6"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi nāma suddhaṃ vatthaṃ apagatakāḷakaṃ sammadeva rajanaṃ "
"paṭiggaṇheyya;"
msgstr "Just as a clean cloth rid of stains would properly absorb dye,"

msgctxt "dn5:114.7"
msgid ""
"evameva kūṭadantassa brāhmaṇassa tasmiññeva āsane virajaṃ vītamalaṃ "
"dhammacakkhuṃ udapādi:"
msgstr ""
"in that very seat the spotless, immaculate vision of the Dhamma arose in the "
"brahmin Kūṭadanta: "

msgctxt "dn5:114.8"
msgid "“yaṃ kiñci samudayadhammaṃ sabbaṃ taṃ nirodhadhamman”ti."
msgstr "“Everything that has a beginning has an end.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="100"></a><a class="wp" id="wp100"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:115.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho kūṭadanto brāhmaṇo diṭṭhadhammo pattadhammo viditadhammo "
"pariyogāḷhadhammo tiṇṇavicikiccho vigatakathaṅkatho vesārajjappatto "
"aparappaccayo satthusāsane bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Kūṭadanta saw, attained, understood, and fathomed the Dhamma. He went "
"beyond doubt, got rid of indecision, and became self-assured and independent "
"of others regarding the Teacher’s instructions. He said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "dn5:115.2"
msgid ""
"“adhivāsetu me bhavaṃ gotamo svātanāya bhattaṃ saddhiṃ bhikkhusaṅghenā”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Would Master Gotama together with the mendicant Saṅgha please accept "
"tomorrow’s meal from me?”"

msgctxt "dn5:115.3"
msgid "Adhivāsesi bhagavā tuṇhībhāvena."
msgstr "The Buddha consented in silence. "

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="101"></a><a class="wp" id="wp101"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:116.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho kūṭadanto brāhmaṇo bhagavato adhivāsanaṃ viditvā uṭṭhāyāsanā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā pakkāmi."
msgstr ""
"Then, knowing that the Buddha had accepted, Kūṭadanta got up from his seat, "
"bowed, and respectfully circled the Buddha, keeping him on his right, before "
"leaving."

msgctxt "dn5:116.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho kūṭadanto brāhmaṇo tassā rattiyā accayena sake yaññavāṭe paṇītaṃ "
"khādanīyaṃ bhojanīyaṃ paṭiyādāpetvā bhagavato kālaṃ ārocāpesi:"
msgstr ""
"And when the night had passed Kūṭadanta had a variety of delicious foods "
"prepared in his own home. Then he had the Buddha informed of the time, "
"saying:"

msgctxt "dn5:116.3"
msgid "“kālo, bho gotama;"
msgstr "“Itʼs time, Master Gotama, the meal is ready.”"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "dn5:116.4"
msgid "niṭṭhitaṃ bhattan”ti."
msgstr " "

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="102"></a><a class="wp" id="wp102"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:117.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya saddhiṃ "
"bhikkhusaṅghena yena kūṭadantassa brāhmaṇassa yaññavāṭo tenupasaṅkami;"
msgstr ""
"Then the Buddha got dressed in the morning and, taking his bowl and robes, "
"went to the home of Kūṭadanta together with the mendicant Saṅgha,"

msgctxt "dn5:117.2"
msgid "upasaṅkamitvā paññatte āsane nisīdi."
msgstr "where he sat on the seat spread out. "

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="103"></a><a class="wp" id="wp103"></a><a
#. class="pts" id="pts1.149"></a>
msgctxt "dn5:118.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho kūṭadanto brāhmaṇo buddhappamukhaṃ bhikkhusaṅghaṃ paṇītena "
"khādanīyena bhojanīyena sahatthā santappesi sampavāresi."
msgstr ""
"Then Kūṭadanta served and satisfied the mendicant Saṅgha headed by the "
"Buddha with his own hands with a variety of delicious foods."

msgctxt "dn5:118.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho kūṭadanto brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ bhuttāviṃ onītapattapāṇiṃ aññataraṃ "
"nīcaṃ āsanaṃ gahetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi."
msgstr ""
"When the Buddha had eaten and washed his hand and bowl, Kūṭadanta took a low "
"seat and sat to one side."

msgctxt "dn5:118.3"
msgid ""
"Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho kūṭadantaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ bhagavā dhammiyā kathāya "
"sandassetvā samādapetvā samuttejetvā sampahaṃsetvā uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkāmīti."
msgstr ""
"Then the Buddha educated, encouraged, fired up, and inspired him with a "
"Dharma talk, after which he got up from his seat and left."

#. </p><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "dn5:119.1"
msgid "Kūṭadantasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
